<div class="info">
  <h3>Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Custom Motor Control Center Configurations</li>
    <li>Comes factory assembled (MCC and controls integrated into module)</li>
    <li>Heating, Air Conditioning, and Ventilation</li>
    <li>Insulated steel base frame & stone aggregate exterior</li>
    <li>Door at each end for emergency egress</li>
  </ul>
</div>

